<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <main>
            <!-- Page Header -->
            <section class="page-header">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>About Nageshwaram Foundation</h1>
                    <p>Dedicated to fostering educational growth and community development in rural India.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Main Content -->
            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <div style="flex: 2; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2>Our Journey of Empowerment</h2>
                            <p>The Nageshwaram Foundation Trust was established with a profound vision: to bring
                                accessible and quality education to the heart of rural India. Founded by visionary
                                educators and philanthropists, our journey began with the understanding that education
                                is the most powerful tool for societal transformation. Since our inception, we have been
                                committed to breaking down barriers to learning and creating pathways to brighter
                                futures for countless children and young adults.</p>
                            <p>Our work extends beyond traditional schooling. We believe in holistic development, which
                                includes academic excellence, character building, skill development, and community
                                engagement. We strive to create an environment where every student feels empowered to
                                explore their potential and contribute meaningfully to society.</p>

                            <h2 style="margin-top: 40px;">Our Guiding Philosophy</h2>
                            <p>At Nageshwaram Foundation Trust, our philosophy is rooted in compassion, integrity, and a
                                relentless pursuit of excellence. We believe in:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Ensuring that quality education reaches every child,
                                    regardless of their socio-economic background or geographical location.</li>
                                <li><strong>Quality Education:</strong> Providing modern learning facilities, qualified
                                    educators, and an updated curriculum that prepares students for the challenges of
                                    tomorrow.</li>
                                <li><strong>Holistic Development:</strong> Nurturing intellectual, emotional, social,
                                    and physical growth, fostering well-rounded individuals.</li>
                                <li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> Working hand-in-hand with parents, leaders,
                                    and community members to create a supportive ecosystem.</li>
                                <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Building educational initiatives that are
                                    long-lasting and continue to serve future generations.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <div
                                style="background: var(--bg-cream); padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);">
                                <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
                                <ul style="list-style: none; margin-left: 0;">
                                    <li style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px 0;">
                                        <strong>Founded:</strong> 2020
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px 0;">
                                        <strong>Location:</strong> Jamui, Bihar
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px 0;">
                                        <strong>Focus:</strong> Rural Education
                                    </li>
                                    <li style="padding: 10px 0;">
                                        <strong>Entities:</strong> School & College
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary"
                                    style="width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">Partner With Us</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>